Uruguay 1948 Championship

Primera A

Final Table:

 1. C Nacional dF                10  8  2  0  29- 6  18 
 2. CA Peñarol                   10  8  1  1  24- 9  17 
 3. CA River Plate               10  5  2  3  20-18  12 
 4. Rampla Juniors FC            10  4  2  4  20-16  10 
