 9. Danubio FC                   10  0  5  5  14-25   5 
10. CA Cerro                     10  1  3  6  12-26   5

Round 1
Peñarol              2-2 Danubio
Nacional             0-0 Central
Montevideo Wanderers 0-3 Rampla Juniors
Cerro                1-1 Liverpool             [*]
River Plate          2-2 Defensor
[*]  the match was originally played at July 18th and suspended at 45' with Cerro leading 1-0.
     The AUF anoulled the match, and it was replayed on September 19th.

Round 2
